Once upon a time in a firest there lived a Crocodile and a Monkey. The Monkey lived on a cherry tree on the banks of a rever.
The crocodile and monkey were friends. The crocodile had a wife.The crocodile came to the banks of the river, under the tree
and the kind hearted monkey offered him some fruits. From that day onwards the crocodile always came back to ruits and they became friends. 
